Dada s World of Hardware on 17 December 2016 held a lucky draw where customers who spent R1 000 between 6 November and 16 December had the chance to win fantastic prizes. Featured photo: Winner of the first prize, a brand new Datsun Go, Charles Manable thanks owner of Dada s World of Hardware, Osman Dada. Second prize winner, Nandi Thahakale is congratulated by Dada s World of Hardware employee, Barbra Sithole on her R10 000 cash prize. Sheryn Dikgale receives the third prize, a 42-inch smart TV, on behalf of third prize winner, Frank Dikgale.